1151
01:27:49,739 --> 01:27:51,364
Sister.

1152
01:27:52,492 --> 01:27:55,409
Good night, Mr Eddington. Mr Lefferts.

1153
01:27:55,537 --> 01:27:58,787
- Jim boy.
- Congratulations.

1154
01:27:58,915 --> 01:28:01,323
I bear you no malice. Mr Babbitt.

1155
01:28:01,751 --> 01:28:05,452
Blasphemy! Good night, Mr Eddington.

1156
01:28:05,588 --> 01:28:09,253
And you... you ought to be
ashamed of yourself.

1157
01:28:23,523 --> 01:28:26,643
Oh, it was... glorious.

1158
01:28:26,776 --> 01:28:30,026
Outrageously, blissfully glorious.

1159
01:28:31,114 --> 01:28:36,820
