going to make up your mind to take it?

1186
01:30:47,167 --> 01:30:49,836
Get in the car. Go on, do as I say.

1187
01:31:07,520 --> 01:31:10,190
Turn on the lights, please.

1188
01:31:29,918 --> 01:31:31,542
There.

1189
01:31:33,046 --> 01:31:35,963
That's what I've been working for.

1190
01:31:36,090 --> 01:31:40,135
No more tents. No more
running around like a circus.

1191
01:31:40,261 --> 01:31:42,883
No more haggling with committees.

1192
01:31:43,598 --> 01:31:45,970
My own tabernacle.

1193
01:31:47,060 --> 01:31:52,054
A permanent home. A clinic for
sick bodies. A free soup kitchen.

1194
01:31:52,190 --> 01:31:56,022
A place of worship for
everybody of every faith.

1195
01:31:57,445 --> 01:31:59,438
That's my first love.

1196
01:32:04,661 --> 01:32:07,199
