1197
01:32:08,790 --> 01:32:11,328
Nothin'. Nothin' at all.

1198
01:32:12,293 --> 01:32:15,745
I'm just a hick from Kansas,
and you're real class, Shara.

1199
01:32:15,880 --> 01:32:20,127
The only class I've got is the name
Falconer. That's why I picked it.

1200
01:32:21,261 --> 01:32:24,215
I'm Katie Jones from shantytown.

1201
01:32:26,516 --> 01:32:29,683
That's right. Shantytown.

1202
01:32:29,811 --> 01:32:35,232
But does that make a liar out of me?
I am Sharon Falconer now. I've made her.

1203
01:32:35,358 --> 01:32:39,605
I've put her together piece by piece
till I've got a right to be her. I am her.

1204
01:32:40,155 --> 01:32:43,440
I started building this tabernacle
two years ago,

1205
01:32:43,575 --> 01:32:47,407
and when this revival is ended,
I'll have enough money to own it.

1206
01:32:47,787 --> 01:32:51,701
Do you think it was blind luck
that brought us to Zenith?

1207
01:32:56,087 --> 01:32:58,127
Do you?

1208
01:32:59,924 --> 01:33:02,083
Of course not.

1209
01:33:02,218 --> 01:33:05,468
- It was God's will.
- Of course.

1210
01:33:14,689 --> 01:33:18,224
- Now do you understand why we...?
- Of course. Of course.

1211
01:33:18,359 --> 01:33:20,933
- Nothing's going to take it away from me.
- Nothing.

1212
01:33:21,070 --> 01:33:23,312
- Nobody must spoil it.
- Nobody.

1213
01:33:24,574 --> 01:33:27,030
- I've never...
- Of course.

1214
01:33:27,160 --> 01:33:29,199
- Never.
- Naturally.

1215
01:33:30,288 --> 01:33:32,328
Yes.

1216
01:33:35,210 --> 01:33:37,167
(man) Sister Sharon?

1217
01:33:37,962 --> 01:33:39,160
Sister Sharon?

1218
01:33:48,306 --> 01:33:51,722
Jim Lefferts is an honourable man.
But so was Brutus.

1219
01:33:51,851 --> 01:33:56,264
