1232
01:34:47,448 --> 01:34:49,774
- Shocking!
- And last night...

1233
01:34:49,909 --> 01:34:56,528
last night, right here on Main Street,
I was accosted by three painted women!

1234
01:34:56,666 --> 01:34:59,584
- The tramps.
