1244
01:35:31,242 --> 01:35:33,650
Some of the preachers
might be against me.

1245
01:35:33,995 --> 01:35:38,324
Unitarianism, Russellism,
Spiritualism - they hate me!

1246
01:35:38,458 --> 01:35:41,459
And what hates me
