1247
01:35:41,586 --> 01:35:44,457
Yaleism, and Princetonism!

1248
01:35:45,465 --> 01:35:48,549
But you're some of God's best people.

1249
01:35:48,676 --> 01:35:51,381
- And you don't hate me, do you?
- No!

1250
01:35:51,513 --> 01:35:55,012
- Smack 'em down, preacher!
- Kill 'em! Murder 'em!

1251
01:36:00,980 --> 01:36:03,222
Can you hear me, Jesus?

1252
01:36:05,276 --> 01:36:10,187
