1268
01:37:31,696 --> 01:37:33,772
(crowd boos)

1269
01:37:34,699 --> 01:37:37,486
But as long as I got a foot, I'll kick booze!

1270
01:37:37,619 --> 01:37:40,370
As long as I got a fist, I'll punch it!

1271
01:37:40,497 --> 01:37:43,533
And as long as I've got a tooth, I'll bite it!

1272
01:37:43,666 --> 01:37:47,249
And when I'm old and grey
and toothless and bootless,

1273
01:37:47,378 --> 01:37:52,717
