and booze goes to hell!

1274
01:37:57,514 --> 01:38:00,135
That's a hell of a speech.

1275
01:38:00,266 --> 01:38:04,845
It's been eight days. It's been eight days
since I gave you the addresses

1276
01:38:04,979 --> 01:38:08,847
