1278
01:38:11,778 --> 01:38:13,569
And what's been done about it?

1279
01:38:13,696 --> 01:38:16,152
- Nothing, Captain.
- (cheering)

1280
01:38:18,535 --> 01:38:21,986
We're gettin' sick and tired of scoldin' sin.

1281
01:38:22,121 --> 01:38:24,410
