1318
01:41:34,355 --> 01:41:36,728
- From me to you.
- ..the circus.

1319
01:41:37,901 --> 01:41:40,308
Shara, you shouldn't have.

1320
01:41:40,445 --> 01:41:44,277
How about you sneaking away
with Katie Jones on a real fun picnic?

1321
01:41:44,407 --> 01:41:47,112
No telegrams,
no newspapers, no sermons.

1322
01:41:47,243 --> 01:41:50,244
The only business of the day will be us.
Just the two of us.

1323
01:41:50,371 --> 01:41:51,996
Oh, Shara.

1324
01:41:53,082 --> 01:41:55,704
- We can't.
